object.script:
function onTick() gear=input.getNumber(1) end
colw=5 rowh=6 function ct(y,str) screen.drawText((w-#str*colw)/2,y,str) end
function onDraw() local gearname w=screen.getWidth() h=screen.getHeight() cx=w/2 cy=h/2
screen.setColor(0,255,0)
if gear==-1 then gearname="R" elseif gear == 0 then gearname="N" else gearname=tostring(gear) end
ct(cy-rowh,gearname) ct(cy+rowh,"GEAR") end
